7T09:34:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.getreadyhk.com/hong-kong-events/hongkong-daytrip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.getreadyhk.com%2Fhong-kong-events%2Fhongkong-daytrip&d=Aqh3AviE8OJ44wl0vSHkdEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=01a5a9fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.getreadyhk.com/hong-kong-events/hongkong-daytrip</a><br />\n<br />\n香港一天遊<br />\n其實仲有好多選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6807532c2e77824ced2aeeb93356579209e71e5","tid":905600,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442993560d1d9697c3fb3cfb03ac9ca40d0e083b","tid":905600,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b06c96e3e45ebea7b12182fc5c4efb9dc9de27","tid":905600,"uid":49697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:27:29.000Z","msg":"兄弟 牛迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95e62e1185873f77843dc9899ae02b990951d84","tid":905600,"uid":120678,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"介唔介紹佢地西貢萬柱海岸好呀<br />\n等佢地行山跌落懸崖都好<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.superbookcity.com/media/catalog/product/cache/1/image/9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95/9/7/9789881971180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.superbookcity.com%2Fmedia%2Fcatalog%2Fproduct%2Fcache%2F1%2Fimage%2F9df78eab33525d08d6e5fb8d27136e95%2F9%2F7%2F9789881971180.jpg&h=64098cf8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f8c306a33c266b44a453c6f9b992fff554cafb8","tid":905600,"uid":17182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"6666666666"},{"pid":"f06f24491baf39cf3a602a336a300578e980b416","tid":905600,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eb5313bede6706a93942d13c44b50d2705ca2cc","tid":905600,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLet&rsquo;s go to HELL together!"},{"pid":"917521cd65675b6c3780338ddc47b112dd9bca7c","tid":905600,"uid":30647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:40:08.000Z","msg":"貼返過呢邊新 post <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>明星聚居加多利山</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n加多利山是在九龙中心市旺角区旁的一个小山坡，是香港非常著名的富人区。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>明星风水居住地</strong><br />\n加多利山大都是独立屋苑，虽然邻近旺角闹市，但小山坡地势较高，有树林绿化带，而且没有地铁公车直达，形成一个隐秘豪宅小区。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20121124/large/v76-hk-144pn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20121124%2Flarge%2Fv76-hk-144pn.jpg&h=31854c19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有风水研究指，加多利山突起的山坡可承接邻近的旺角闹市人气，更有两条主干道环抱，被视为九龙最佳风水豪宅地之一，因此吸引城中不少富豪、名人明星大腕都居住在此，包括天后陈慧琳, 郑伊健, 吴君如, 成龙, 胡杏儿, 导演徐克，就连天王刘德华一家三口的大宅也在这里。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dERJG1F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdERJG1F.png&h=53891896&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加多利山空气也满新鲜的，随意走走，蛮悠闲的，适合去放松放松。这里还可一窥明星们的门户，幸运的话还可跟明星打个照脸，是一个偶遇名人的好地方。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如何前往</strong><br />\n港铁东铁线旺角东站D出口步行5分钟即达，亚皆老街往东走，沿嘉道理道往上走。"},{"pid":"b25ec7f94e2a1de65584a68efb4d87650205218a","tid":905600,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:45:37.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdfc1db96715ae92b6cbf747faf1187605b8e96","tid":905600,"uid":174432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"有冇遊記版？好似重呃到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a993d61a84fe013cc82728821719947fb9ab36","tid":905600,"uid":5948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae37c9fcc84409944a425fdad93b97403beb731","tid":905600,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfe7386e07e7f55a4213463cc012a40cc14aae1","tid":905600,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99310717cb71cf423c18faffb718ffbf37214b89","tid":905600,"uid":35648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"頂<br />\n樓主好人一生平安"},{"pid":"efad73b65fbe4b0f9e5970167d9a61aa0a32863e","tid":905600,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a5139839254eb601e81871f96b781da37c6cad","tid":905600,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T06:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma